OL,3,CAurigny to investigate alleged
OL,4,Cdefamatory comments
OL,6,FGuernsey's airline Aurigny has
OL,7,Flaunched an investigation after a
OL,8,Fstaff member allegedly referred to
OL,9,Fwheelchair customers as "lame and
OL,10,Flazy".
OL,12,FThe comments came to light from an
OL,13,Fanonymous whistleblower who alleges
OL,14,Fthey were made on Wednesday 4
OL,15,FSeptember during a staff meeting.
OL,17,FDuring a discussion about wheelchair
OL,18,Fpassengers, a member of staff
OL,19,Fallegedly referred to them as "lame
OL,20,Fand lazy", adding that half of said
OL,21,Fpassengers did not need them.
