OL,6,FAt the same online meeting, another
OL,7,Femployee was allegedly heard saying
OL,8,F"Leave them and let them burn" when
OL,9,Fasked how to help disabled customers
OL,10,Fin the case of a fire.
OL,12,FThe whistleblower explains: "This is
OL,13,Fabsolutely disgusting, and I was
OL,14,Fshocked to my core at what I was
OL,15,Fhearing from both of them. I trust a
OL,16,Fthorough investigation will be carried
OL,17,Fout."
OL,19,FAn Aurigny spokesperson says it is
OL,20,Fconsidering the allegations and what
OL,21,Faction, if any, is appropriate.
