OL,3,CAurigny to investigate alleged
OL,4,Cdefamatory comments
OL,6,FDr Rob Harnish, Managing Director at
OL,7,FGuernsey-based disability charity Ron
OL,8,FShort Centre (UnLtd), hopes any
OL,9,Finvestigation is "handled sensitively".
OL,11,FWhile he wouldn't comment on specific
OL,12,Fallegations, he explains: "What we
OL,13,Fwant is for people who may have made
OL,14,Fcomments like this to actually
OL,15,Funderstand better what they've said.
OL,17,F"So many of us are upset. The idea is
OL,18,Falways to decrease the amount of
OL,19,Fignorance in society and to create a
OL,20,Fgreater cohesive community."
