OL,3,CAurigny to investigate alleged
OL,4,Cdefamatory comments
OL,6,FAn Aurigny spokesperson states: "We
OL,7,Fhave received an anonymous email
OL,8,Fmaking certain allegations. We have
OL,9,Fasked the sender for further
OL,10,Finformation but have had no response.
OL,12,F"Notwithstanding this, we have already
OL,13,Finitiated an internal investigative
OL,14,Fprocess in accordance with our
OL,15,Finternal policies. This will consider
OL,16,Fthe allegations and consider what
OL,17,Faction, if any, is appropriate."
OL,19,FThey add that there will be no further
OL,20,Fcomment while the investigation is
OL,21,Funderway.
